text: "Nasty" is a 1986 song by Janet Jackson and is the second single from her third studio album Control. It went to number 3 in the United States, number 19 in the United Kingdom, number 5 in the Netherlands, number 8 in New Zealand, Canada and Switzerland, number 17 in Finland and Australia and number 9 in Germany. ==Track listings== *US, UK, and European 7-inch single :A.
